title: Hour 2 - Draymond Green Video Leaked, Kevin Millar
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Draymond Green Video Leaked, Kevin Millar
description:
Dan and the Danettes react to the newly leaked video of Draymond Green punching teammate Jordan Poole at Golden State Warriors practice. And former MLB player and current analyst Kevin Millar stops by to break down the MLB playoffs as the Wild Card round starts today.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
